==Verb==
#To employ a nail as a fastener to join objects together.
#(''slang'') To catch.
#(''slang'') To expose as a sham.
#(''slang'') To accomplish something completely.  ''I really '''nailed''' that test.''
#(''slang'') To hit a target effectively with some weapon.

